                  <.cp class="text-sm">
                    The Mishka card component is ideal for displaying content in a clean, organized layout. Whether for portfolios, product listings, or user profiles, it offers customizable options for size, color, and design. Perfect for enhancing your web projects with ease and flexibility.
                  </.cp>
                </.card_content>
                <.card_footer padding="large">
                  <.button variant="outline" full_width color="silver" size="small">
                    See more
                  </.button>
                </.card_footer>
              </.card>

              <.card variant="shadow" rounded="large" color="natural">
                <.card_media src={~p"/images/mishka-chelekom-media-2.jpg"} alt="Mishka chelekom" />
                <.card_content padding="large" class="text-center">
                  <h2 class="font-bold text-lg">Customizable</h2>
                  <.cp class="text-sm">
                    The Mishka card component is ideal for displaying content in a clean, organized layout. Whether for portfolios, product listings, or user profiles, it offers customizable options for size, color, and design. Perfect for enhancing your web projects with ease and flexibility.
                  </.cp>
                </.card_content>
              </.card>

              <.card space="small" rounded="large">
                <.card_title class="border-b border-[#E5E7EB]" padding="small" position="between">
                  <div>Flexible</div>
                  <.button
                    size="extra_small"
